can contemporary R&B singers]]\n[[Category:American dance musicians]]\n[[Category:American dancers]]\n[[Category:American expatriates in Japan]]\n[[Category:American female dancers]]\n[[Category:American female pop singers]]\n[[Category:American pop singers]]\n[[Category:American film actresses]]\n[[Category:American people of Ecuadorian descent]]\n[[Category:American sopranos]]\n[[Category:American soul singers]]\n[[Category:American stage actresses]]\n[[Category:American television actresses]]\n[[Category:American voice actresses]]\n[[Category:American women activists]]\n[[Category:American women record producers]]\n[[Category:Brit Award winners]]\n[[Category:Child pop musicians]]\n[[Category:Dance-pop musicians]]\n[[Category:Dancers from New York (state)]]\n[[Category:Feminist musicians]]\n[[Category:Grammy Award winners]]\n[[Category:Hispanic and Latino American actresses]]\n[[Category:Hispanic and Latino American female singers]]\n[[Category:HIV/AIDS activists]]\n[[Category:Latin Grammy Award winners]]\n[[Category:Latin pop singers]]\n[[Category:LGBT rights activists from the United States]]\n[[Category:Record producers from New York (state)]]\n[[Category:Mouseketeers]]\n[[Category:Music video codirectors]]\n[[Category:Musicians from Pittsburgh]]\n[[Category:Participants in American reality television series]]\n[[Category:People from Rochester, Pennsylvania]]\n[[Category:People from Staten Island]]\n[[Category:RCA Records artists]]\n[[Category:Record producers from California]]\n[[Category:Record producers from Pennsylvania]]\n[[Category:Sex-positive feminists]]\n[[Category:Singers from Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:Singers from New York City]]\n[[Category:Singers from Pennsylvania]]\n[[Category:Singers with a four-octave vocal range]]\n[[Category:Sony BMG artists]]\n[[Category:Women in Latin music]]\n[[Category:World Food Programme people]]\n[[Category:MTV EMA winners]]\n[[Category:World Music Awards winners]]\n", "name_user": "Bi-on-ic", "label": "unsafe", "comme