ber of DVDs featuring one episode from a variety of the animated television series they have produced, including \"[[Shimmer & Shine]]\", \"[[Blaze and the Monster Machines]]\", \"[[Blue\u2019s Clues]]\", \"[[Bubble Guppies]]\", \"[[Dora and Friends: Into the City!]]\", \"[[The Fresh Beat Band of Spies]]\", \"[[Paw Patrol]]\", \"[[Rusty Rivets]]\", \"[[Sunny Day (TV series)|Sunny Day]]\", \"[[Top Wing]]\" and \"[[Wallykazam!]]\", 6 on each DVD.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=\"1\"\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:green; color:yellow; font-size:100%\" align=\"center\" |\n|-\n! DVD Name\n! Episodes\n! Release Date\n|-\n| Nick Jr: Big Birthday Bash\n|\n* \"Boom Zahra-Bake\"\n* \"Masquerade Charade\"\n| \n* [[DVD Region Code|Region 1]]: June 4, 2019<ref>{{cite web|title=Nick Jr: Big Birthday Bash \u2502 DVD (Region 1)|date=June 4, 2019|ASIN=6317815186|URL=https://raru.co.za/movies-tv/7375140-nick-jr-big-birthday-bash-region-1-dvd|website=Raru|publisher=Nickelodeon / Paramount|access-date=29 April 2020}}</ref><REF>https://www.walmart.com/ip/821762494</REF>\n* [[DVD Region Code|Region 2]] (UK): July 15, 2019<ref>{{cite web|title=Nick Jr: Big Birthday Bash \u2502 DVD (Region 2 - UK)|date=15 July 2019|id=Amazon-ASIN=https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B07TDG21B8  B07TDG21B8|URL=https://www.fishpond.com.au/Movies/Nick-Jr-Big-Birthday-Bash/5053083196028|website=Fishpond|publisher=Nickelodeon / Paramount|access-date=29 April 2020}}</ref><REF> https://raru.co.za/movies-tv/7792736-nick-jr-big-birthday-bash-dvd</REF>\n* [[DVD Region Code|Region 4]]: August 28, 2019<ref>{{cite web|title= Nick Jr: Big Birthday Bash \u2502 DVD (Region 4)|date=28 August 2019|id=Amazon-ASIN=[https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B07RLHNTH7 B07RLHNTH7]|URL=https://www.bigw.com.au/product/nickelodeon-junior-s-big-birthday-bash/p/57233/|website=JB Hifi|publisher=Nickelodeon / Universal Sony|access-date=29 April 2020}}</ref> \n|-\n| Nickelodeon Favorites: Whiskers & Paws\n| \n* \"Abraca-Genie\"\n| \n* [[DVD Region Co