nt|access-date=15 April 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n[[Nickelodeon]], with [[Paramount Home Media Distribution|Paramount]] for [[DVD Region Code|Region 1]] and with [[Universal Pictures Home Entertainment|Universal]] / [[Sony Pictures Home Entertainment|Sony]] for [[DVD Region Code|Region 4]], released a number of DVDs featuring one episode from a variety of the animated television series they have produced, including \"[[Shimmer & Shine]]\", \"[[Blaze and the Monster Machines]]\", \"[[Blue\u2019s Clues]]\", \"[[Bubble Guppies]]\", \"[[Dora and Friends: Into the City!]]\", \"[[The Fresh Beat Band of Spies]]\", \"[[Paw Patrol]]\", \"[[Rusty Rivets]]\", \"[[Sunny Day (TV series)|Sunny Day]]\", \"[[Top Wing]]\" and \"[[Wallykazam!]]\", 6 on each DVD.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=\"1\"\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:green; color:yellow; font-size:100%\" align=\"center\" |\n|-\n! DVD Name\n! Episodes\n! Release Date\n|-\n| Nick Jr: Big Birthday Bash\n|\n* \"Boom Zahra-Bake\"\n* \"Masquerade Charade\"\n| \n* [[DVD Region Code|Region 1]]: June 4, 2019<ref>{{cite web|title=Nick Jr: Big Birthday Bash \u2502 DVD (Region 1)|date=4 June 2019|id=Amazon-ASIN=[https://www.amazon.com/dp/6317815186 6317815186]|URL=https://www.amazon.com/dp/6317815186|website=Amazon|publisher=Nickelodeon / Paramount|access-date=9 April 2020}}</ref>\n* [[DVD Region Code|Region 4]]: August 28, 2019<ref>{{cite web|title=Nick Jr: Big Birthday Bash \u2502 DVD (Region 4)|date=28 August 2019|id=JBHiFi-SKU=[https://www.jbhifi.com.au/products/nickelodeon-juniors-big-birthday-bash-2019-dvd 391910]|URL=https://www.bigw.com.au/product/nickelodeon-junior-s-big-birthday-bash/p/57233|website=JB Hifi|publisher=Nickelodeon / Universal Sony|access-date=9 April 2020}}</ref>\n|- \n|-\n| Nickelodeon Favorites: Whiskers & Paws\n| \n* \"Abraca-Genie\"\n| \n* [[DVD Region Code|Region 1]]: January 26, 2016<ref>{{cite web|title=Nickelodeon Favorites: Whiskers & Paws \u2502 DVD (Region 1)|id=Amazon-ASIN=[https://www.amazon.com